'''Tinawt n Ajdir''' (s [[Tutlayt Taɛṛabt|taɛrabt]]: خطاب أجدير) tga yat tinawt bahra istawhman ɣ tmazirt n Lmɣrib d umzruy n tutlayt tamaziɣt. Ass n 17 ktubr 2001 ɣ tmdint n [[Ajdir]], inna ugllid akswat [[Muḥmmad VI|Muḥmmad wiss ṣḍiṣ]] is ''"Tamaziɣt, d adasil axatar n tdlsa tamɣrabiyt"''. Irna ɣ wawal nns; inna: ''"Asmɣr n tmaziɣt iga tamasayt tanamurt"''. Iqqan d i imzdaɣn akkʷ n tmazirt ad amun ɣ usmɣr n tmagit nnsn. 

Zɣ wass nna, tkcm tmaziɣt azmz amaynu. Tinawt n Ajdir, tṛẓm idirn imqqurn i [[Tutlayt tamaziɣt tanawayt tamɣribit|tmaziɣt]]: tkcm tinml, ttwarayn as idlisn s iskkiln n tfinaɣ, tettwaslmd tjṛṛumt d tussna nns. Acku tirra ayd isbddan tutlayt f iḍaṛn nns. Tirra ad as yakkan ad tzri zɣ tsuta s tsuta s tussna nns. Zun d idirn, tṛẓm tinml zun d winna ṛẓmn imassn n umsawaḍ, lumn ttilifizyun. ilmma, tinawt n ajdir tga asurif imqqurn ɣ ubrid n izrfan n ufgan. Acku, zun d wawal zun d tmazirt, iqqan d ad tn nḥḍu d ad tn nssmɣur.<ref>''Tifawin a Tamaziɣt'' - Aswir wis 3 n uslmd amnzu. tasna. 60 [https://www.abudrar.com/2014/10/tifawine-a-tamazight-3.html <nowiki>[Ɣr ɣ wantirnit]</nowiki>]</ref>

